19:09.226 --> 19:10.927
I should go.
Yeah.

19:11.762 --> 19:14.063
Uh, thank you
for the drink.

19:14.065 --> 19:16.566
No problem.

19:16.568 --> 19:17.450
(sighs)

19:17.452 --> 19:19.402
Hey, Stuart.
Yeah?

19:19.404 --> 19:22.622
Do you want to...
hang out tomorrow night,

19:22.624 --> 19:25.291
maybe grab a bite to eat
or catch a late movie?

19:25.293 --> 19:29.111
Yeah, I-I'd like to,
but I'm a little tight on funds.

19:29.113 --> 19:30.630
No problem. My treat.

19:30.632 --> 19:32.215
I'll swing by after work.

19:32.217 --> 19:33.500
Okay.

19:33.502 --> 19:35.134
Okay.

19:38.956 --> 19:41.841
I could do worse.

19:46.629 --> 19:48.165
BERNADETTE: <i>Aw, that's such</i>
<i>good news, Howie.</i>

19:48.166 --> 19:49.565
<i>Thank you for telling her.</i>

19:49.567 --> 19:52.685
Hey, I'm a grown man;
I'm gonna live with my wife.

19:52.687 --> 19:57.106
My mother's just gonna have
to learn to make do on her own.

19:57.108 --> 19:58.891
Was she upset?

19:58.893 --> 20:02.261
Who can tell?
She yells everything.

20:03.814 --> 20:06.065
She might have been upset.

20:06.067 --> 20:08.701
She might have been hungry.

20:08.703 --> 20:11.154
Thanks for fixing it.

20:11.156 --> 20:12.655
I love you.

20:12.657 --> 20:13.906
I love you, too.

20:13.908 --> 20:15.908
Sweet dreams.
I'll talk to you tomorrow?

20:15.910 --> 20:18.778
Good night, Rocket Man.

20:18.780 --> 20:21.447
To infinity and beyond, baby.

20:21.449 --> 20:22.882
(clicks tongue)

20:24.017 --> 20:25.451
Loops.

20:25.453 --> 20:27.954
You realize you just
lied your ass off

20:27.956 --> 20:30.056
to your wife
<i>and</i> your mother.

20:30.058 --> 20:31.424
I know.

20:31.426 --> 20:33.543
What are you gonna do
when you get back to Earth?

20:33.545 --> 20:34.894
Oh, I'm never going back.

